thread.title: Worker’s body found hanging from rope in school
thread.title_full: Worker’s body found hanging from rope in school | New York Post

author: Larry Celona
title: Worker’s body found hanging from rope in school
text:
The body of a school maintenance worker was discovered hanging from a rope in the basement of PS 106 in Brooklyn on Sunday evening, according to police.
Cops say a coworker discovered the 56-year-old man hanging from a pipe and called 911.
Emergency responders tried to revive him to no avail. He was pronounced dead at the scene.
The incident appeared to be a suicide, authorities said.
